title: Classmates
subTitle: A group of college friends meet after many years for a class reunion. However, due to some unexpected turn of events, several dark secrets are revealed, which changes their lives.

title: Thinkal Muthal Velli Vare
subTitle: A famous television scriptwriter vows never to get married. However, he is forced into marriage by one of his ardent fans who threatens to commit suicide if he does not marry her.

title: Aayudham
subTitle: When a powerful explosion occurs at the Vilayam beach seconds after Chief Minister Madhavan leaves the venue, Police Officer Rishikesh is tasked with the investigation to find the truth behind the blast.

title: Honey Bee
subTitle: A man proposes to his close friend on the night before her wedding. However, he incurs the wrath of her older brothers when he elopes with her.

title: Kadha Parayumbol
subTitle: Balan, a barber, struggles to give his family a better living. However, his life changes when his old friend, who is a film star, comes to his village for a film shoot.

title: Natturajavu
subTitle: Pulikkattil, an affluent family man, is forced to bear the brunt and burden of his late father's unscrupulous past. Now, Karnan, a jail convict, decides to settle some old scores with him.

title: Hridayam
subTitle: Arun, a young man, enrols in an engineering college but falls prey to bad habits. As he grows up, he decides to turn over a new leaf and become a responsible adult.

title: Chovvazhcha
subTitle: While investigating mysterious suicides in a village, a sub-inspector of police realises that they are murders in reality.

title: Sthanarthi Sreekuttan
subTitle: Sreekuttan and Ambadi present an intense rivalry concerning a school election. Soon, the contest fundamentally affects the classroom and involves pride and friendship.

title: Philips and the Monkey Pen
subTitle: Ryan Philip is a mischieveous 8-year-old, struggles with math- and his strict teacher Pappan. However, everything changes when he discovers a magical pen that helps him solve all his problems.

title: Philips and the Monkey Pen
subTitle: Ryan Philip is a mischieveous 8-year-old, struggles with math- and his strict teacher Pappan. However, everything changes when he discovers a magical pen that helps him solve all his problems.

title: Idiots
subTitle: A wealthy heiress plans to implicate her former boyfriend for her murder by hiring an assassin. Things take a turn when a thief enters the house at the same time.

title: Aattam
subTitle: Karthick is an easygoing college student who falls in love with Thenmozhi, a village girl. However, when he professes his love to her, she turns him down in favour of pursuing her ambitions.

title: Maharaja Talkies
subTitle: Vimala and her three sisters run a theatre called Maharaja Talkies. They get in trouble when Pappachan, a rich man, forces Vimala to shut down the theatre.

title: Varathan
subTitle: After losing his job, Aby and his wife, Priya, move back to the latter's family estate in Kerala. However, things go from bad to worse for the couple as they encounter a new set of challenges.

title: Kalippattam
subTitle: A violinist enters a marriage that promises security, only to face heartbreak as love, illness and time reshape everything he once believed was under control.

title: RDX
subTitle: Robert, Dony and Xavier grow up together while honing their fighting skills. However, after an incident separates them for several years, an attack on their family reunites the three friends.

title: In Ghost House Inn
subTitle: Thomas Kutty buys a haunted bungalow and convinces his friends to stay with him on the first night. The trouble begins when they actually see the ghost of the mistress who was killed 70 years ago.

title: Return Of The Dragon
subTitle: Reeling from a sad breakup, a college student gives up on his studies to commit financial fraud. However, his new endeavour puts him in a difficult spot.

title: Oru Yamandan Premakadha
subTitle: Lallu, a happy-go-lucky person who loves to hang out with his friends, is in pursuit of true love. One day, he finds a photo of a missing woman, Diya, in the newspaper and feels a spark.

title: Oru Yamandan Premakadha
subTitle: Lallu, a happy-go-lucky person who loves to hang out with his friends, is in pursuit of true love. One day, he finds a photo of a missing woman, Diya, in the newspaper and feels a spark.

title: Bharya Athra Pora
subTitle: Priya is furious to learn that her alcoholic husband, Sathyanadhan, is in love with Neena. Things deteriorate further after she files for divorce and her family takes some foolish steps.

title: Love
subTitle: The unhealthy relationship between a man and his wife spirals out of control after a fight, revealing previously unknown aspects of their personalities.

title: Nakhangal
subTitle: Three friends, living in a rented house owned by an NRI, get entangled in a conspiracy when a fourth person moves in, bringing conspiracy and unforeseen trouble.

title: Rasathanthram
subTitle: Premachandran, a carpenter, rescues Kanmani, an ill-treated maid, and takes her into his care. However, to escape from her former abusers, Kanmani dresses up as a boy and joins the team of carpenters.

title: Happy Husbands
subTitle: The lives of three happily married men are turned upside down by the arrival of a bar singer. They are later reunited during a holiday in Malaysia.

title: Thuruppugulan
subTitle: Menon buys land for his five-star hotel and asks his trusted employee, Sreedharan Unnithan, to take its charge. Years later, Unnithan gets Menon imprisoned in a fake case and Kunjumon helps him.

title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: Christian Brothers
subTitle: When the daughter of a minister gets kidnapped, Christy is called upon to rescue her. Although he manages to save her, he himself gets embroiled in the kidnapper's murder.

title: Chunkzz
subTitle: The lives of four friends Romario, Riyas, Yoodas and Athmaram, take a dramatic turn when a girl joins their mechanical engineering class.
